{
  "number": 5140,
  "html_url": "https://github.com/algolia/instantsearch/issues/5140",
  "title": "FR: add `<label>` to menuSelect",
  "body": "A `<select>` without a `<label>` is not very user friendly and not good from a a11y perspective.\r\nhttps://developer.mozilla.org/en-US/docs/Web/HTML/Element/select\r\n\r\nPlease add a parameter to the userSelect widget, that outputs this.\r\n\r\n## CURRENT OUTPUT\r\n```\r\nmenuSelect({\r\n\tcontainer: '#menu-select',\r\n\tattribute: 'brand'\r\n})\r\n```\r\n\r\n```\r\n<div class=\"ais-MenuSelect\">\r\n\t<select class=\"ais-MenuSelect-select\">\r\n\t\t<option class=\"ais-MenuSelect-option\" value=\"\">See all</option>\r\n\t\t<option class=\"ais-MenuSelect-option\" value=\"Brand1\">Brand1</option>\r\n\t\t<option class=\"ais-MenuSelect-option\" value=\"Brand2\">Brand2</option>\r\n\t</select>\r\n</div>\r\n```\r\n\r\n## FUTURE OUTPUT 1\r\n```\r\nmenuSelect({\r\n\tcontainer: '#menu-select',\r\n\tattribute: 'brand',\r\n\tlabel: 'Brands'\r\n})\r\n```\r\n\r\n```\r\n<div class=\"ais-MenuSelect\">\r\n\t<label>\r\n\t\tBrands\r\n\t\t<select class=\"ais-MenuSelect-select\">\r\n\t\t\t<option class=\"ais-MenuSelect-option\" value=\"\">See all</option>\r\n\t\t\t<option class=\"ais-MenuSelect-option\" value=\"Brand1\">Brand1</option>\r\n\t\t\t<option class=\"ais-MenuSelect-option\" value=\"Brand2\">Brand2</option>\r\n\t\t</select>\r\n\t</label>\r\n</div>\r\n```\r\n\r\n## FUTURE OUTPUT 2\r\n```\r\nmenuSelect({\r\n\tcontainer: '#menu-select',\r\n\tattribute: 'brand',\r\n\tlabel: 'Brands',\r\n\tid: 'brands'\r\n})\r\n```\r\n\r\n```\r\n<div class=\"ais-MenuSelect\">\r\n\t<label for=\"brands\">Brands</label>\r\n\t<select class=\"ais-MenuSelect-select\" id=\"brands\">\r\n\t\t<option class=\"ais-MenuSelect-option\" value=\"\">See all</option>\r\n\t\t<option class=\"ais-MenuSelect-option\" value=\"Brand1\">Brand1</option>\r\n\t\t<option class=\"ais-MenuSelect-option\" value=\"Brand2\">Brand2</option>\r\n\t</select>\r\n</div>\r\n```",
